
Scanned synthesis is related to → Kunst/Musik/Theory/synthesis/wave-table-synthesis: the wave table is changed at sub audio frequence (< 15 Hz, aka *haptic rates*).

Scanned synthesis emphasises the performer's control of → Kunst/Musik/Theory/timbre.



